
What is the problem?
Products are not tailered and advertised in a way attractive to diffrent types of demoographic, this causes a reduction in sales due to the lack of attention by the customer.
The cause.
It is caused due to the lack of market segmenation and resources to segment the market, often times it is expensive to conduct primary research this is as, for example, data packages advertised are too general instead of specific rendering the advertising usless
